# execution-loop.mdc

- Global execution flow is mandatory: requirements -> tmp -> releases -> plans -> build -> validate -> review -> release-check
- Always follow implementation loop: Build -> Test -> Validate -> Refine/Fix -> Repeat
- If Refine/Fix repeats fail more than 2-3 iterations on the same issue, switch to instrumentation-first debugging (temporary logs/prints/probes), gather evidence, and continue the loop only after root cause is identified
- Do not skip steps
- Do not stop at build
- Do not stop at passing tests
- Done means proven done
